<mehj@mail.vetmed.lsu.edu>
[The cost for multiple animals or for people who routinely travel as well
as anesthetic risk for elderly animals is inappropriate. As such it would
appear to be totally a scheme for financial gain. Microchipping can be used
for tracking vaccinations which would make tattooing unnecessary. The
British require the microchipping, so the tattooing is obsolete, especially
since they even admit to it wearing off. It is an ineffective tracking
system. - Mod.TG
